{"tid":1593781,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際連線，幫我推上熱門】今晚八點中大和聲書院有聲援新疆學者集會！","createTime":"2019-09-25T08:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T13:39:52.000Z","uid":9322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"324ed8a6a999c7ef4e779c7c932d5c124045c2e4","tid":1593781,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"今次嘅集會係同新疆、維吾爾人we connect，等大家明白香港人唔係淨係關心自己，亦都係關注緊中共打壓，同時關注人權問題！<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚八點和聲書院！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1pG4tU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1pG4tU.jpg&h=9754b820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解係喺成日畀人笑鳩嘅和聲書院搞？</span></strong><br />\n係因為和聲書院曾經同新疆醫科大學簽咗交流計劃，過往亦有中大同學去同新醫大嘅學生互相交流。新醫大仲送咗刻字嘅石頭畀和聲，放咗喺書院門前。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日，面對新疆醫科大學前校長吾甫爾教授將被處決，中大校方及書院唔肯表態，就等學生話畀外界聽，我哋一直關注事件！但學生唔夠人，需要大家support！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日新疆，明日香港！今日放工放學一齊去和聲書院集會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原POST推唔上，求大家推我上熱門！<br />\n【國際連線】9.25中大集會 聲援新疆學者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1589936/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1589936/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：九月二十五日（星期三）<br />\n時間：晚上八點<br />\n地點：中文大學和聲書院石碑"},{"pid":"1ea900791942aba51f80082b629639bf266ebd73","tid":1593781,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0c6bb26f737d405f6f9709fbeec2082d5a3d020","tid":1593781,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8978b0f901fdafa42789c8